column5: I thought i recognized your avatar on page 18 of the new Ontario out of doors......and my suspicions were correct,  good work
Well done,but that little girl kicked yer butt, with that huge crappie.LOL
Oh great I'm fishing this week with a celebrity. Will your head fit inside the plane?

No kidding, it's in the mag???   I haven't even gotten my copy in the mail yet...  Gotta give Dave (JDMLS) credit, he took the pic, I just caught the fish  Mike, I'll sign your rod if you want, just let me know bud
I am from the same town as Bill.  I have never met him but we have PM'd a few times. It is great living in the midst of stardom.
NOPE!!!! Better see how much for a twin Otter!!!!
Bill I didn't know you swung that way. Not that there's anything wrong with that.
LMAO!!!!!!  You guys are killing me.
Acch! Yer right! He's got a huge cranium, it's like an orange on a toothpick!!  Ah, poor wee lad, he'll be cryin' his eyes out tonight if he reads this...ON HIS HUGE PILLOW!!
Classic. S-A-T-U-R-D-A-Y NIGHT!  There's a piper down!  Head, pants, now!
No it's Friday morning, you missed the flight.
Mike's favourite movie... I think he recited the whole thing the last time we went fishing
HEHE! Didn't know if anyone would get that. I think we'd get along just fine LOL!
You guys are too funny! A lil giddy about the trip it seems lol!
